# Cursor chat export log (dev session transcript, not documentation).
# Note: docs/archive/cursor-chat-exports/ is NOT ignored - it was already
# committed to git history before this rule existed, so ignoring it here
# would only stop new changes from being tracked, not remove the existing
# 6.7MB blob from history. That needs a deliberate history-rewrite pass,
# same as the customer invoice PDF noted in docs/roadmap.md.
docs/archive/cursor_git_sync_completion_status.md

